{"tid":1727264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"巴士觀塘繞道自炒撞壆　10多人受傷","createTime":"2019-11-16T11:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:22:48.000Z","uid":216992,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd8564451ae61fbdd8f58232263dde2e7c888b14","tid":1727264,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"九龍灣發生車禍。今晚(16日)6時許，一輛九巴沿觀塘繞道往旺角方向行駛，駛至近麗晶花園對開時，巴士懷疑失控自炒撞壆，車頭嚴重損毀。初步消息指，事件造成車上10多人受傷，消防及救護員正在場救援，事件仍待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ww8XpKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWw8XpKa.jpg&h=b6686ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhX1Rpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhX1Rpd.jpg&h=c5bff238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191116/bkn-20191116185706162-1116_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191116%2Fbkn-20191116185706162-1116_00822_001.html&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=86b31e05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191116/bkn-20191116185706162-1116_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"31f491b770e9fc08b381b0fdaf97801bf8dbc133","tid":1727264,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b11ea758ceeee44b1fb793f6e32a66c6f902f5","tid":1727264,"uid":62708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"屌 一定係佔中影響啦！"},{"pid":"6ec9d0219456428027bc29932f25cb053e63cee3","tid":1727264,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"希望無人重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0affe8d07de7c1e85b839797c235e2d45ae503d","tid":1727264,"uid":67348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"